EventListExpressionProxy, SimpleExpressionProxy
public abstract class ExpressionProxy
extends ElementProxy

The abstract base class of all expressions. This is the abstract base class of all expressions that may occur in a module. This includes the expressions in package net.sourceforge.waters.model.expr as well as the special event list expressions (EventListExpressionProxy) that are specific to modules.

Author:
Robi Malik
